body:
@dandar I wrote some more docs on how to use `rclone config backend -o config drives gdrive:` here: https://rclone.org/drive/#drives

> Nick, can we somehow mount all remotes at once?

You are talking about being able to mount remotes at a given path. What we'd do is add a new `-o mount` outut which would build an rclone config for an as yet nonexistent `mount` backend, which could then show the shared drives in the right places.
